   <taskbody>
      <prereq class="- topic/section task/prereq ">
         <p class="- topic/p ">Before you start the battery circuit test check: <ul class="- topic/ul ">
               <li class="- topic/li ">
                  <p class="- topic/p ">That the settings for the test is correct.</p>
               </li>
               <li class="- topic/li ">
                  <p class="- topic/p ">That the battery is connected.</p>
               </li>
               <li class="- topic/li ">
                  <p class="- topic/p ">That the battery breaker is closed.</p>
               </li>
               <li class="- topic/li ">
                  <p class="- topic/p ">That the rectifier modules are in float charge.</p>
               </li>
            </ul>
            <note class="- topic/note ">It is not possible to start the test with the rectifier
modules in boost charge (charge), equalization charge or battery operation
(batterytest).</note>
         </p>
      </prereq>
      <steps class="- topic/ol task/steps ">
         <step conref="M_How_to_Start_the_Relay_Tests_TSK_0000752494.dita#HowToStartTheRelayTests-FD3177D6/M_User-Access_Service"
               class="- topic/li task/step ">
            <cmd class="- topic/ph task/cmd "/>
         </step>
         <step id="FromTheMenuBarNavigateToServiceDCSy-0057E33A"
               class="- topic/li task/step ">
            <cmd class="- topic/ph task/cmd ">Press
the <uicontrol class="+ topic/ph ui-d/uicontrol ">Main menu icon</uicontrol> and navigate to <uicontrol translate="no" class="+ topic/ph ui-d/uicontrol ">Service &gt; Reality Modular DC 1 &gt; Battery tests</uicontrol>.</cmd>
         </step>
         <step class="- topic/li task/step ">
            <cmd class="- topic/ph task/cmd ">Press the <uicontrol translate="no" class="+ topic/ph ui-d/uicontrol ">Start</uicontrol> button
in line with <uicontrol translate="no" class="+ topic/ph ui-d/uicontrol ">Start battery circuit test</uicontrol> to start the test.</cmd>
            <info class="- topic/itemgroup task/info ">
               <image href="../Images/Battery-tests_0000755264.png"
                      placement="inline"
                      class="- topic/image "/>
            </info>
         </step>
      </steps>
      <result class="- topic/section task/result ">
         <p class="- topic/p ">This test does not discharge the battery, it only checks
that the battery is correctly connected to the circuit.</p>
         <p class="- topic/p ">If the
voltage stays above the set voltage level for the set time, the battery
circuit test is successful.</p>
         <p class="- topic/p ">In case the voltage drops below
the set voltage level at any time, the test is interrupted and considered
unsuccessful.</p>
      </result>
